text = "Welcome to the WoodChopper! Your objective is to chop wood effectively using your axe while managing its durability. You have an axe and a piece of wood to chop. The axe's durability is crucial; too much force can damage it. Too weak of a force doesn't quite chop the wood! To play, tap and hold on the screen to charge your swing's strength. The longer you hold, the stronger the swing. Each piece of wood has a strength requirement indicated by a colored square at the top right corner in the game. The colors signify the wood strength index going from the weakest to the toughest: Green, Blue, Orange, Red, and Gold. To successfully chop the wood, match the strength indicated by the color without exceeding it, as overchopping can damage your axe. Find the right balance of strength to achieve maximum efficiency and enjoy chopping wood in this challenging game!"
